    {
      "id": "PopularPost145112",
      "post_content": "Use in conjunction with [lullmage mentor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lullmage mentor) to spawn some merfolk for your countered spells, with this card allowing much better control decks. You can use the merfolk tokens to either counter your opponents spells via lullmages ability or as sack fodder to make the ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) counterspells worthwhile and cost the same as [Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell) but with the bonuses of the extra abilities. some examples of the spells are [rewind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=rewind), [scattering stroke](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=scattering stroke), [summoners bane](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=summoners bane), [fuel for the cause](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=fuel for the cause), [dismiss](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=dismiss), [dismal failure](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=dismal failure), [discombobulate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=discombobulate) and [last word](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=last word). Each spell you counter will give you fuel to sacrifice for your next spell, with a win condition of your own choice.",
      "posted_by": "jsttu",
