    {
      "id": "PopularPost89032",
      "post_content": "Very Rakdos flavor, but this card might gain the best benefit from Galgari guild, such as Bloodbond March.  \n  \nThe biggest flaw I see here is that creature is the easiest of all permanents to destroy. One sweeper, you won't be able to play non-creature spells till you have another creature out.",
